      <title>《华尔街日报》称习近平下周将在北京会见美国高管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/xi-to-meet-with-us-executives-in-beijing-next-week-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，中国国家主席习近平计划下周在北京举行年度论坛期间会见多位美国商界领袖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/xi-to-meet-with-us-executives-in-beijing-next-week-wsj-says</guid>
